latestIgtvVideos.caption:
No Ramayan Mahabharat. Keeping it Short and simple but special. 
I have always been cribbing for an elder sister since childhood but God decided to grany me this wish 3 years ago!!!! Strangers -> College Senior-> Friends-> Best friends -> Sisters.
 This journey has been amazing 💯

I wish your life be filled with good surprises, lots of free healthy khaana, eyeshadow palettes and most important ME 💁‍♀️. I miss your hugs, I miss our stupid irrelevant talks, I miss us getting ready together, I miss your sisterly advice I just miss everything about you. Be happy and stay blessed .

Yours lovingly,
Pumpkin 🤭🎃 PS- Mahabharat likh hi diya 🙈
